ingredients:
*KEY INGREDIENTS*

- Vitamin C
Vitamin Cis an essential addition to this essence for its ability to firm up the skin. It can smoothe out wrinkles and fine lines and as a bonus, its antioxidant qualities offer protection from harmful UV rays from the sun.

- Vitamin F
Within this essenceâ€™s formula, vitamin F is called upon to encourage skin cell growth as well as moisture. It keeps your skin moist as well as youthfully elastic.

- Quinoa seed extract
Extracted from the quinoa grains, quinoa seed extract provides excellent moisture and protection from free radical damage. Your skin not only becomes supple thanks to it, but also firm and smooth as any threatening free radicals are fought.

- Date palm seed extract
From the towering date palm tree comes this seed extract, an antioxidant powerhouse that thoroughly fights off any active free radicals. It is an anti- aging treasure trove that keeps the skin smooth and elastic.

- Glutathione
As part of this essence formulation, glutathione is a very potent skin brightening agent. Any dark circles or overall dullness become a thing of the past as your eyes light up with that welcoming radiance.

- Acetyl Tetrapeptide-5
Last but certainly not least is Acetyl Tetrapeptide-5, a synthetic peptide that is able to soothe and hydrate the skin upon application.

Niacinamide, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Glyceryl Linoleate, Glyceryl Oleate, Glyceryl Linolenate
